text: Stupica or Stupitsa (; Cyrillic: Ступица) is a Slavic surname that means a trap, wheel hub assembly. It may refer to *Marija Lucija Stupica (1950-2002), Slovene children's book illustrator *Marlenka Stupica (born 1927), Slovene children's book illustrator, mother of Marija *Mira Stupica (1923–2016), Serbian actress
title: Stupica
